{"title":"寄居他乡感怀","authors":["刘蓄雄"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄居他乡感怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘蓄雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依忍把故园抛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海角飘零忆故交。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自笑不如梁上燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年一度一归巢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜阑人静月三更，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独卧思亲梦不成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几度徘徊灯畔下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知何日是归程。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}